==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Years purchase
<hw>Year's purchase</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>The amount that is yielded
by the annual income of property; -- used in expressing the value of a
thing in the number of years required for its income to yield its
purchase price, in reckoning the amount to be paid for annuities,
etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Yearth</ent>⟦br⟧
